foreignData.name: Schutzkreis gegen Grün

mainBoard.name: Circle of Protection: Green
mainBoard.originalText: {1}: Prevents all damage against you from one green source. If a source does damage to you more than once in a turn, you must pay 1 mana each time you want to prevent the damage.

rulings.text: A source of damage is a permanent, a spell on the stack (including one that creates a permanent), or any object referred to by an object on the stack. A source doesn’t need to be capable of dealing damage to be a legal choice.
Can be used even when there is no damage to prevent. It prevents the next damage (if any) from the source this turn.

mainBoard.text: {1}: The next time a green source of your choice would deal damage to you this turn, prevent that damage.
